net.olioinfo.fileutils
Class CombinedPropertyFileLoader

java.lang.Object
  net.olioinfo.fileutils.CombinedPropertyFileLoader

public class CombinedPropertyFileLoader
extends java.lang.Object

Find all the property files in the specified trees, and load them all into a single Properties instance.

For example:

 Properties combinedProps = CombinedPropertyFileLoader.loadAndCombineProperties(System.getProperty("user.dir"),"test-props.properties");

will load all the property files named 'test-props.properties' in the tree rooted at 'System.getProperty("user.dir")' ('user.dir' is usually the directory active when the JVM is started).
